channel.title: DaWuAutoFighter V 1.11
channel.description:
So here it is, My very own autofighter.
It: AutoEats Fights (Lawl) AntiBan AntiRandoms Login Logout
Works great, DON'T USE ON CROWDED PLACES, IT WORKS SLOWLY, BECAUSE IT TAKES MORE TIME TO SEE ARE YOU IN FIGHT IF SOMEONE ELSE IS FIGHTING. So don't use on too crowded places, such as goblin house etc. Already gained over 300k xp with it nonbanned. Have fun AND GIVE ME SOME FEEDBACK <3
